description:
I had trouble uploading this due to it's length, but it is finally here. Pause has got me hooked on playing this game. It is very fun and addicting. I recommend you watch the tutorial before attempting to join a game because there is a lot to learn, and you won't enjoy playing it as much if you don't understand how it works.

Note: Most of the time this game has a dragon boss fight at night, but if rob is not around assassins are chosen instead.
